Embattled businessman and NASA operative Jimmi  Wanjigi today once again found himself in an embarrassing situation after police surrounded his vehicle on the streets in a dramatic attempt to serve him with summons to appear in a Nyeri court.
Drama ensued after Wanjigi refused to heed orders to stop and disembark from his vehicle, forcing the police to paste the court summons on the  windscreen,requiring him to appear in court tomorrow to face criminal charges. 